        Create an ElementRef
        Parameters:
        ws - the XmlDataWorkspace where the element reference is created
        eTag - the XmlDataElementTag of the referenced element
        min - the minimum number of occurrences
        max - the maximum number of occurrences
        useFieldRef - - a flag, if true, uses an NSFieldRef; if false use an NSRecordRef.
